recentProperties.description: Developed by Sobha Real Estate LLC, Coral Beach Villas is a gated residential community situated on the scenic Sobha Siniya Island near Umm Al Quwain. This project, which offers an unmatched level of luxury and comfort, is a component of the first phase of the broader Sobha Siniya Island development. A delivery date for the Coral Beach Villas project will shortly be revealed. The property is currently under construction.
